{{obsolete}}

{{flavour|This spell causes weapons on the ground near the caster to all leap into the air and dance together.}}

'''Tukima's Ball''' is a monster-only spell which causes all weapons in your [[line of sight]] to become hostile [[dancing weapon]]s, as though you'd cast [[Tukima's Dance]] on a [[curse]]d weapon. It can only be cast by [[Terpsichore]] (who is also [[obsolete]]).

<!--[[Category:Monster Spell]]-->
